txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Lethal sharp claws from the turtles surrounding Tyrn Lhuig. Delivery of the items should be made to Othran at the base of the hilltop outpost.
'If our numbers were greater, we would have larger supplies of worm claws. Alas, we must rely on others to aid us still.'
Council of the North Task: Lethal Sharp Claws
The hunters at Tyrn Lhuig expect a delivery of lethal sharp claws to be made to Othran, one of their number at the bottom of their hillside outpost.
Deliver the lethal sharp claws to Othran at Tyrn Lhuig in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver lethal sharp claws from the turtles surrounding Tyrn Lhuig to Othran at the bottom of the hillside outpost.
Wanted: Lethal sharp claws from the turtles surrounding Tyrn Lhuig.
